name.jp: カボチャ男爵の売り子くん

description.en: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.ar: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.br: É Halloween! Esse Sr. Abóbora gerência uma Loja Pessoal para você! Dê clique duplo para fechar a Loja. Você recebe o item de volta quando a loja é fechada.
description.cns: 现在是万圣节！ 这位南瓜先生可以为您管理你的个人商店！ 双击他来关闭商店。
description.de: Es ist Halloween! Dieser Mr. Pumpkin verwaltet deinen Laden für dich! Doppelklicke um ihn zu schließen.
description.fi: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fil: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.fr: C'est Halloween! Ce Pumpkin s'occupe d'une Boutique Personnelle pour vous ! Double-cliquez pour fermer la Boutique. Vos objets vous seront rendus.
description.id: Ini Halloween! Mr. Pumpkin ini mengelola Personal Shop untuk Anda! Klik dua kali untuk menutup Shop. Anda mendapatkan barang kembali saat Shop tutup.
description.it: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.jp: ハロウィンですよ～！このカボチャさんが個人商店を代行してくれます！バフアイコンでダブルクリックすると閉じることができ、アイテムを取り戻します。
description.kr: 할로윈이군요! 미스터펌킨이 여러분을 위해 개인 상점을 관리합니다! 상점을 닫으려면 두 번 클릭하세요. 상점이 닫히면 아이템을 돌려받습니다.
description.nl: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.pl: Jest Halloween! Ten Pan Dynia zarządza dla Ciebie osobistym sklepem! Kliknij dwukrotnie, aby zamknąć Sklep. Otrzymasz przedmioty z powrotem po zamknięciu Sklepu.
description.ru: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.sp: ¡Es Halloween! ¡Este Mr. Pumpkin atiende tu Tienda Personal por tí! Doble click para cerrar la Tienda. Recuperarás el objeto cuando se cierre la Tienda.
description.sw: It's Halloween! This Mr. Pumpkin manages a Personal Shop for you! Double click to close the Shop. You get the item back when the Shop is closed.
description.th: มันเป็นวันฮาโลวีน! Mr. Pumpkinคนนี้จัดการร้านค้าส่วนตัวให้คุณ! ดับเบิ้ลคลิกเพื่อปิดร้าน ได้ของคืนเมื่อร้านปิด
description.tw: 萬聖節!南瓜先生來幫你管理個人商店，雙擊可以關閉商店，商店關閉時將會返回物品
description.vi: Đó là Halloween! Ông Pumpkin này quản lý một Cửa hàng cá nhân cho bạn! Nhấp đúp để đóng Cửa hàng. Bạn nhận lại hàng khi Shop đóng cửa.
